parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden detachment of interior trim and panels can cause distraction, injury, or even accidents due to obstructed visibility or physical harm to occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden opening of the hood while driving can obstruct visibility, cause loss of control, and lead to accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake issues can cause the vehicle to take longer to stop, increasing the risk of accidents.
